					  	<strong>Good News!</strong><br><br>
					    It looks like USA is providing some aid to its citizens during these trying times. It has been reported that ome major health insurers have promised to cover care and testing related to COVID-19. A number of celebrities and professional athletes have donated significant resources to help those taking a financial hit by the pandemic, such as the workers at the stadiums where athletes play. And there are more! Amid all the doom and gloom, there are some positive stories, positive messages and reasons to remain hopeful.
