				  <h2>New Zealand</h2>
					<p>
					  	<strong>Champions of proper resonse to pandemic</strong><br><br>
					    New Zealand is now known for their coordinated response and prevention of the Covid-19 pandemic. They were successful in closing everything immediately, with strict rules and regulations for its citizens. Unlike other places, where people are going to beaches, or going to a park with 10000 people, New Zealanders were very cautious. Hence the decreased reported cases and the relieving lift on restrictions.
